{"tid":2431416,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV音樂頒獎禮全民投票","createTime":"2021-03-03T15:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T15:30:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19fee9d022f5b6b89f50da0ca9097ca410429fd5","tid":2431416,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210303/7YBN6ZCP5BHS5A23QO4KT77ZAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210303%2F7YBN6ZCP5BHS5A23QO4KT77ZAE%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX6g2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=7207a319\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210303%2F7YBN6ZCP5BHS5A23QO4KT77ZAE%2F&h=f299da9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210303/7YBN6ZCP5BHS5A23QO4KT77ZAE/</a><br />\n<br />\nViuTV音樂頒獎禮全民投票<br />\n<br />\nViuTV首個音樂頒獎禮《Chill Club推介榜 年度推介20/21》將於下月18日在九展舉行，林二汶、鄭欣宜、陳柏宇、李幸倪（Gin Lee）、江海迦、泳兒、許廷鏗及MIRROR等多位歌手，昨日在九龍灣出席頒獎禮記者會，大會公佈11個獎項候選名單，除作曲人等四個幕後獎項外，所有獎項均由全港市民一人一票方式投票選出。<br />\n<br />\n對於無綫日前跟三大唱片破冰，會否擔心被分薄各大唱片公司上ViuTV的意欲？ViuTV高層金廣誠說：「唔會，大家各有各做。」對於無綫藝人王君馨有份獲提名女歌手等獎項，金生表示有邀請對方出席頒獎禮，被問到會否讓星夢歌手派歌上榜，他直言：「Why Not？」他更不介意公司藝人MIRROR及ERROR亮相無綫節目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5FH0Uk2HBPSI_UNIi9_keAU6m5o=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QRIIK6WLRVBPFFNHLXPSNP4HZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5FH0Uk2HBPSI_UNIi9_keAU6m5o%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQRIIK6WLRVBPFFNHLXPSNP4HZE.jpg&h=861072c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Gin Lee有份入圍女歌手獎，她直言Chill Club像她第二個家，有幸可以參加到第一屆頒獎禮，成為歷史一部份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cSdJgW9Cuu8bVN6hmt5TrGRmReg=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HDDI2OVECFEXBLADOXFZYCJQIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcSdJgW9Cuu8bVN6hmt5TrGRmReg%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHDDI2OVECFEXBLADOXFZYCJQIQ.jpg&h=a64ed193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■ViuTV親生仔MIRROR獲得最多提名，姜濤還入圍除女歌手獎外的所有獎項。"}]}